<h3 id="makeempty-this" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#makeempty-this" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box2.makeEmpty" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">makeEmpty<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> () : this</h3>
<p>使此盒子为空。</p>
<h3 id="set-min-vector2-max-vector2-this" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#set-min-vector2-max-vector2-this" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box2.set" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">set<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( min : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector2<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>, max : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector2<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ) : this</h3>
<p><a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">min<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> - (必须) 表示该盒子的下边界(x, y)。
