<h3 id="setfromcenterandsize-center-vector2-size-vector2-this" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#setfromcenterandsize-center-vector2-size-vector2-this" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box2.setFromCenterAndSize" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">setFromCenterAndSize<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( center : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector2<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>, size : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector2<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ) : this</h3>
