<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">size<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> - 盒子所要设置的x和y尺寸 (<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector2<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>).</p>
