<h3 id="setfrompoints-points-array-this" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#setfrompoints-points-array-this" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box2.setFromPoints" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">setFromPoints<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( points : Array ) : this</h3>
<p>points - 点的集合，由这些点确定的空间将被盒子包围。</p>
